data.description: Unique completely renovated townhome,  nestled in the heart of Palm Beach Gardens. The screened in patio is an oasis to paradise, perfect for your entertainment or bbq family dinners.Recent renovations include 42 inch. kitchen cabinets, new flooring through out the house , including the patio, new balcony surface,  partial impact windows, stainless steel appliances, Ac unit.  White tiled floors on the living area. Engineered flooring in bedrooms, roll on window shades, redone bathrooms with new vanities.Master suite with built in closet organizer in the spacious walk in closet.Community offers a swimming pool.Nothing to do to this home for years to come.Easy access to shopping, major roads and the beach.
